---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import heroImage from "../assets/home/gareth-winter-home-1.JPG";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
	<title>Roadbook of Cycling</title>
	<meta name="description" content="Performance, craft, and the quiet obsession of getting better." />
</head>

<body>
	<header class="site-header">
		<nav>
			<a href="/" class="active">Home</a>
			<a href="/blog">Blog</a>
			<a href="/about">About</a>
		</nav>
	</header>

	<main class="home">
		<section class="home-inner">
			<div class="home-text">
				<span class="eyebrow">Roadbook of Cycling</span>

				<h1>Performance, craft, and the quiet obsession of getting better.</h1>

				<p class="lede">
					I write from inside the sport. Where training meets equipment.
					Where detail becomes confidence. Where progress is earned, not claimed.
				</p>

				<ul class="pillars">
					<li>I write from inside the sport.</li>
					<li>Where training meets equipment.</li>
					<li>Where detail becomes confidence.</li>
					<li>Where progress is earned, not claimed.</li>
				</ul>

				<p class="signal">Minimal hype. Maximum signal.</p>

				<div class="actions">
					<a href="/blog" class="btn-primary">Read the writing</a>
					<a href="/about" class="btn-secondary">About</a>
				</div>

				<div class="credibility">
					<p class="credibility-lead">
						I’ve spent over a decade inside elite performance environments.
					</p>

					<p>
						Former Creative Director at Team Sky, working alongside Olympic champions
						and Grand Tour winners. Contributor to systems that delivered Olympic gold
						medals, Tour de France and Giro d’Italia victories.
					</p>

					<p>
						Now leading creative strategy and performance systems at Mindvalley,
						focused on human optimisation and transformation at global scale.
					</p>

					<p class="credibility-signoff">
						Cyclist. Creative leader. Student of marginal gains.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="home-image">
				<Image
					src={heroImage}
					alt="Gareth Winter at a time trial event"
					width={900}
					height={1200}
					loading="eager"
				/>
				<span class="caption">
					Real-world training. Real-world constraints. Real-world obsession.
				</span>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<style>
		body {
			margin: 0;
			font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
			color: #111;
			background: #fff;
		}

		.site-header {
			border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
			padding: 1rem 2rem;
		}

		nav {
			max-width: 1200px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			display: flex;
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}

		nav a {
			text-decoration: none;
			color: #555;
			font-weight: 500;
		}

		nav a.active {
			color: #000;
			border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
			padding-bottom: 0.25rem;
		}

		.home {
			padding: 4rem 2rem;
		}

		.home-inner {
			max-width: 1200px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
			gap: 4rem;
			align-items: start;
		}

		.eyebrow {
			text-transform: uppercase;
			letter-spacing: 0.08em;
			font-size: 0.7rem;
			color: #666;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			line-height: 1.15;
			margin: 0.75rem 0 1.5rem;
		}

		.lede {
			font-size: 1.05rem;
			line-height: 1.5;
			color: #333;
			max-width: 36rem;
		}

		.pillars {
			margin: 1.5rem 0;
			padding-left: 1.2rem;
		}

		.pillars li {
			margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		}

		.signal {
			font-weight: 500;
			margin: 1.25rem 0;
		}

		.actions {
			display: flex;
			gap: 1rem;
			margin: 2rem 0;
		}

		.btn-primary {
			background: #000;
			color: #fff;
			padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
			border-radius: 999px;
			text-decoration: none;
			font-weight: 500;
		}

		.btn-secondary {
			border: 1px solid #ccc;
			color: #000;
			padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
			border-radius: 999px;
			text-decoration: none;
			font-weight: 500;
		}

		.credibility {
			margin-top: 2rem;
			max-width: 36rem;
			font-size: 0.95rem;
			color: #333;
		}

		.credibility-lead {
			font-weight: 600;
			margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		}

		.credibility-signoff {
			color: #666;
			margin-top: 0.75rem;
		}

		.home-image img {
			width: 100%;
			height: auto;
			display: block;
		}

		.caption {
			display: block;
			margin-top: 0.5rem;
			font-size: 0.75rem;
			color: #666;
		}

		@media (max-width: 900px) {
			.home-inner {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			}
		}
	</style>
</body>
</html>